        <li><p><url href="https://math.libretexts.org/Bookshelves/Linear_Algebra/Linear_Algebra_with_Applications_(Nicholson)/05%3A_Vector_Space_R/5.03%3A_Orthogonality/5.3E%3A_Orthogonality_Exercises">Nicholson 5.3.6(b)</url></p></li>
